research_municipality_step.notes: Canton, TX operates as a General Law Type A city with a Council/Manager form of government, which falls under the 'mayor_council' type. Councilmembers are elected at large. There was a minor discrepancy in the Mayor's last name (Everett vs. Berry), with 'Lou Ann Berry' appearing in the most recent listings. One source incorrectly listed Joe Gunter as Mayor.
